# Protei_Bulk Change Log

## Version 1.0.0 (2025-01-16)

### Initial Release

#### New Features:
- ✓ SMPP 3.4 protocol support
- ✓ HTTP REST API for message submission
- ✓ Campaign management system
- ✓ Real-time CDR generation
- ✓ Multi-protocol support
- ✓ Message queue management
- ✓ User authentication and authorization
- ✓ Role-based access control
- ✓ Message templates
- ✓ Bulk message submission
- ✓ Campaign scheduling
- ✓ Message status tracking
- ✓ Delivery receipts
- ✓ Performance monitoring
- ✓ Log management and rotation

#### Infrastructure:
- ✓ PostgreSQL database support
- ✓ MySQL database support
- ✓ Redis caching
- ✓ High availability configuration
- ✓ Load balancing support
- ✓ Horizontal scaling capability

#### Management Scripts:
- ✓ start - Start application
- ✓ stop - Stop application
- ✓ restart - Restart application
- ✓ reload - Reload configuration
- ✓ status - Check service status
- ✓ version - Display version info

#### Utility Scripts:
- ✓ backup_db.sh - Database backup
- ✓ rotate_logs.sh - Log rotation
- ✓ check_license.sh - License validation
- ✓ cleanup_tmp.sh - Temporary file cleanup

#### Configuration Files:
- ✓ app.conf - Application settings
- ✓ db.conf - Database configuration
- ✓ log.conf - Logging configuration
- ✓ protocol.conf - Protocol settings
- ✓ network.conf - Network configuration
- ✓ security.conf - Security settings

#### Documentation:
- ✓ Installation Guide
